title: Morning sighting near Pelican Lake
observed: Northern Wisconsin: We saw something big, smelly, and brown with long straggly hair and after 20 plus years it's like yesterday.  I  took foot castings and gave them to the DNR but never heard back. It was not a bear, it walked away from us very fast but did not run.
location_details: Logging road near Indian land and creek deep in the woods
